	** IMPORTANT **: In December 2011 Zoovy announced a new one page checkout application that will offer
a majority of buyers a superior checkout experience.  Unfortunately the new
technology is not compatible with 100% of the wrappers and themes, so it
cannot be used by all clients.   Our intention is to release additional
functionality throughout the 2012 year that will enhance both the checkout
and shopping experience and then terminate support for the existing checkout
on January 1st, 2013 - giving clients a full year to transition.  Update: This deadline has been extended till March 2013.
	</div>
