	<b>One Page Checkout notes:</b>
	<ul>
	<li> You should select the one page checkout which is compatible with your customer account behavior.
	<li> The setup checkout application, requires Javascript. 
	<li> Not compatible with all wrappers (specifically incompatible with prototype javascript framework) including bluelicious, shoptastic, evolution.
	<li> Requires Asynchronous Google Analytics code to be installed/configured properly.
	<li> One Page Checkouts 2012.02.xx and later use the popular jQuery-UI theme style conventions, 
			the checkout can be stylized using a custom Jquery-UI theme, a default style is provided.
	</ul>

	<div class="hint">
	NOTE: Additional Checkout Apps are planned for release later in 2012. 
	</div>
	</td>
